n>0
a_n\to3
\sqrt{a_n}\to\sqrt{3}
|\sqrt{a_n}-\sqrt{3}|<|a_n-3|
\varepsilon>0
N\in\Bbb N
n>N
\varepsilon>0
\sqrt{a_n}\to\sqrt{3}
n\to\infty
|\sqrt{a_n}-\sqrt{3}|<|a_n-3|<\varepsilon
\sqrt{a_n}>0
\sqrt{3}>1
\sqrt{a_n}+\sqrt{3}>1
|\sqrt{a_n}-\sqrt{3}|\cdot1<|\sqrt{a_n}-\sqrt{3}|\cdot|\sqrt{a_n}+\sqrt{3}|=|a_n-3|
a_n-3=(\sqrt{a_n}-\sqrt 3)(\sqrt{a_n}+\sqrt 3)\Longrightarrow
\left|\sqrt{a_n}-\sqrt 3\right|=\frac{|a_n-3|}{|\sqrt{a_n}+\sqrt3|}
